<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.round() PJH</h2>

<p>Math.round(x) returns the value of x rounded to its nearest integer:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = Math.round(4.4);
</script>

</body>
</html>

// ROUND => 반올림과 같음 가까운 정수표기


*


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.pow() PJH</h2>

<p>Math.pow(x,y) returns the value of x to the power of y:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = Math.pow(8,2);
</script>

</body>
</html>


// pow(a,b) => a^b


*


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.abs() PJH</h2>

<p>Math.abs(x) returns the absolute (positive) value of x:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = Math.abs(-4.4);
</script>

</body>
</html>


// abs = 절대값

*


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.ceil() PJH</h2>

<p>Math.ceil() rounds a number <strong>up</strong> to its nearest integer:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = Math.ceil(4.4);
</script>

</body>
</html>


// ceil => 올림
// floor -> 내림
// min , max(배열) => 배열안의 값들 중 최소 최대 값 표기
// math.sin , cos , tan 등 삼각함수와 뿐만아니라 random 도 가능





